[2026-03-08 14:30:16]    Response: {"name": "Compare Equipment NG", "summary": "A mod that displays side-by-side item cards, similar to Diablo and Borderlands, comparing a selected item with all equipped items on you or your followers that it would replace.", "description": "[b][color=#00ffff][size=3]Description[/size][/color][/b]\n<br />Armor mods often use only one of Skyrim\u2019s 32 body slots meaning you can have many different armor pieces equipped at once. This can make it tedious to compare a new item against your equipped armor, especially if you have a large inventory or the item has multiple slots that would replace several equipped pieces. This mod displays side-by-side item cards, allowing you to directly compare stats and effects between the selected item and all equipped items (yours or your followers\u2019) that it would replace.\n<br />\n<br />As mentioned above, this mod functions for both the player and your active followers. Additionally, it will work in the inventory menu, container menu, barter menu, QuickLoot IE's loot menu, and on equipment in-world. It will not currently work in the crafting menu. Also, this mod should be compatible with all other UI mods as long as SkyUI is installed.\n<br ...
